# __PLUGIN_TITLE__

Generated plugin scaffold for Ghost shell runtime.

- Use `definePlugin()` from `@ghost-shell/contracts` for your manifest.
- Use `defineReactParts()` from `@ghost-shell/react` for React-based parts.
- Use hooks (`useGhostApi`, `usePluginContext`) instead of prop drilling.
- Use `var(--ghost-*)` CSS custom properties for all colors. Never hardcode hex values.
